1. If you have not already, download the BOSH manifest as instructed in the [Download the BOSH Manifest](http://docs.pivotal.io/pivotalcf/customizing/backup-settings.html#manifest) section.

1. Run `bosh deployment DEPLOYMENT-MANIFEST` to set your deployment.
    <pre class="terminal">
    $ bosh deployment cf.yml
    Deployment set to `/home/working_directory/cf.yml'
    </pre>


1. To view the list of VMs in your selected deployment, run 
<pre class='terminal'>$ bosh VMs</pre>
Notice that all the Cloud Controller VMs begin with "cloud\_controller".
